{"tid":927310,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★微軟Win 10將“砍掉”Edge換上Anaheim瀏覽器","createTime":"2018-12-04T05:38:46.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-07T16:06:38.000Z","uid":19454,"like":21,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":41,"replies":[{"pid":"41cbab22758d89190f69fdb6a7c85d230bd79884","tid":927310,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T05:38:46.000Z","msg":"IT之家12月4日消息 雖然Windows 10系統在全球的份額節節攀升，但是內置的Edge瀏覽器份額卻呈現長期低迷狀態，而微軟內部也在權衡Edge的去留。外媒Windows Central報導，微軟正在打造一款基於谷歌Chromium引擎的瀏覽器，取代現有的EdgeHTML渲染引擎。<br />\n<br />\n報告稱，微軟正在打造新的基於谷歌Chrome使用的Chromium的渲染引擎取代EdgeHTML渲染引擎，這將導致網絡瀏覽器更加兼容，減少維護工作量。<br />\n<br />\n消息稱，內部代號為Anaheim（阿納海姆）的瀏覽器將於2019年初開始進入Insider預覽通道，並將在Windows 10 19H1系統中完成，最終將完全取代Edge瀏覽器。<br />\n<br />\n微軟已經將Chromium用於Edge for Android瀏覽器，而遷移到Chromium將會節省資源，並且意味著將能夠支持為Chrome瀏覽器編寫的擴展。然而，新的問題是瀏覽器的Shell界面。 EdgeHTML引擎在Windows 10上已經提供了比Chrome瀏覽器更流暢的體驗，但是功能上還不成熟。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ithome.com/0/398/340.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ithome.com%2F0%2F398%2F340.htm&d=NYmES5WDJcQ8v5dh30qlYxv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=cdc0ffd6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ithome.com/0/398/340.htm</a>"},{"pid":"84d33b54d0750dce0388c3929c258a4df1a84ede","tid":927310,"uid":48362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T05:39:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a0d1008597f096def17f4344a1a2832e351d0cd","tid":927310,"uid":19454,"like":44,"dislike":1,"score":43,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T05:40:11.000Z","msg":"執柒左佢啦"},{"pid":"5405d46cf649574764d210cefc1717197f0f4e86","tid":927310,"uid":36901,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T05:40:24.000Z","msg":"早就要啦"},{"pid":"7bd0b3e711aee4c2523827fecddead3d21b62988","tid":9