br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ithome.com/0/398/340.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ithome.com%2F0%2F398%2F340.htm&d=NYmES5WDJcQ8v5dh30qlYxv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=cdc0ffd6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ithome.com/0/398/340.htm</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T11:10:17.000Z","msg":"整番間Anaheim Electronic 仲好啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3afed33ac5469063e5df092110076206aad1a3df","tid":927310,"uid":89514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T12:26:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d13fafafabf61f3fda2e10f61ad22b0a7bcb7592","tid":927310,"uid":5220,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T12:32:17.000Z","msg":"Edge個死症係用藍e做logo<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2df98e17b2c66afcf5de6765b133cd4d68f8eb5","tid":927310,"uid":20414,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a9616930f112577c2f75db6e614f6e938ae82d2c","tid":927310,"uid":45148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"926d0f6c05ae266ef68acf58efd77b72dfe99bbb","tid":927310,"uid":156913,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T09:51:53.000Z","msg":"用過edge,  除咗少plugin外無乜野， load得都快<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n定係就係因為無乜野， 所以無誘因轉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T09:54:44.000Z","msg":"我覺得佢播youtube順過chrome<br />\n尤其係少ram 低階機"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T12:44:48.000Z","msg":"究竟上面有幾多人未用過<br />\n慳 ram 慳電對 touch screen 完善支援<br />\nchrome 食屎啦"},{"pid":"d1b8c04b43c33da7d9bd30d7f5a507750f265ee3","tid":927310,"uid":20414,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"3afed33ac5469063e5df092110076206aad1a3df","tid":927310,"uid":89514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T12:26:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除